{"tid":689773,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《美女廚房》最新一輯負評如潮　5大無法超越上輯的不足之處","createTime":"2018-06-04T10:16:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T15:03:52.000Z","uid":66943,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a27a97d99a58a3f689e11b0678ad1beebd8d946c","tid":689773,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T10:16:40.000Z","msg":"《美女廚房》全新一輯終於出街，節目由製作到播出都有很多反對聲音，而第一集公開之後，負評依然不斷。看來珠如在前，最新一輯要超越的話實在有很大距離，改進的地方有不少，就為大家數數五大缺點位。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/w600/201806/20180604122243_21_PCPU18040-2018-jun-4-037.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2Fw600%2F201806%2F20180604122243_21_PCPU18040-2018-jun-4-037.jpg&h=604984b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/w600/201806/20180604122243_22_PCPU18040-2018-jun-4-051.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2Fw600%2F201806%2F20180604122243_22_PCPU18040-2018-jun-4-051.jpg&h=8e2b45aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《美女廚房》相關文章：<br />\n<br />\n不可再現的經典畫面！新版《美女廚房》請唔到的特別嘉賓<br />\n<br />\n《美女廚房》12年後再翻拍　網民要原班人馬先會睇<br />\n<br />\n《美女廚房》地獄廚神變晒做人妻　吳雨霏火燒錄影廠最經典<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>主持人功力有待改進</strong><br />\n今輯由林盛斌、蕭正楠及張振朗做主持，除了阿Bob之外，其餘兩位主持經驗可算少之又少，張振朗更是第一次做主持，節目只見他不太會帶動氣氛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/w600/201806/20180604120343_0_PCPU18040-2018-jun-4-013.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2Fw600%2F201806%2F20180604120343_0_PCPU18040-2018-jun-4-013.jpg&h=7a8ab34a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/w600/201806/20180604120343_1_PCPU18040-2018-jun-4-058.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2Fw600%2F201806%2F20180604120343_1_PCPU18040-2018-jun-4-058.jpg&h=4cfe6ee3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/w600/201806/20180604120343_2_PCPU18040-2018-jun-4-084.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2Fw600%2F201806%2F20180604120343_2_PCPU18040-2018-jun-4-084.jpg&h=b1092dee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相比上兩輯主持鄭中基、方力申及梁漢文，更是缺少幽默感和比較拘謹，看他們試菜有種夾硬話難食的感覺。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/w600/201806/20180604121722_19_20180314170649_3_-2018-mar-14-065.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2Fw600%2F201806%2F20180604121722_19_20180314170649_3_-2018-mar-14-065.jpg&h=234ca9c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/w600/201806/20180604121722_20_20180314170818_9_-2018-mar-14-071.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2Fw600%2F201806%2F20180604121722_20_20180314170818_9_-2018-mar-14-071.jpg&h=3bd5aad1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>沒有重量級嘉賓</strong><br />\n十年前後，TVB的變化實在太大。節目的嘉實的範圍越來越細，如今只有TVB女藝員參與。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/w600/201806/20180604120343_3_PCPU18040-2018-jun-4-040.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2Fw600%2F201806%2F20180604120343_3_PCPU18040-2018-jun-4-040.jpg&h=e58540f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/w600/201806/20180604120343_5_PCPU18040-2018-jun-4-078.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2Fw600%2F201806%2F20180604120343_5_PCPU18040-2018-jun-4-078.jpg&h=b9c205a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/w600/201806/20180604120343_4_PCPU18040-2018-jun-4-052.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2Fw600%2F201806%2F20180604120343_4_PCPU18040-2018-jun-4-052.jpg&h=3006a114&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/w600/201806/20180604120343_8_PCPU18040-2018-jun-4-055.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2Fw600%2F201806%2F20180604120343_8_PCPU18040-2018-jun-4-055.jpg&h=8dec6a18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n縱觀第一集的女嘉賓，陳凱琳與黃心穎都是港姐出身，煮菜時不夠放，又少了觀眾最想睇的蝦碌場面。<br />\n<br />\n你睇下！片頭全部都係TVB女藝員！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/w600/201806/20180604120343_6_PCPU18040-2018-jun-4-004.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2Fw600%2F201806%2F20180604120343_6_PCPU18040-2018-jun-4-004.jpg&h=d11bcc3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/w600/201806/20180604120343_7_PCPU18040-2018-jun-4-001.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2Fw600%2F201806%2F20180604120343_7_PCPU18040-2018-jun-4-001.jpg&h=af0952ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家應該好難請到楊千嬅、鄧麗欣這類的重量級嘉賓。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/w600/201806/20180604121722_17_20180316160141_4_-2018-mar-16-073.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2Fw600%2F201806%2F20180604121722_17_20180316160141_4_-2018-mar-16-073.jpg&h=fa39e267&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/w600/201806/20180604121722_18_20180316160141_0_-2018-mar-16-055.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2Fw600%2F201806%2F20180604121722_18_20180316160141_0_-2018-mar-16-055.jpg&h=31c82f22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>節目玩法沉悶</strong><br />\n今輯《美女廚房》有新玩法，就是需要評審嘉賓猜三位美女是誰人，又要遮樣、聲音經過處理。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/w600/201806/20180604120343_9_PCPU18040-2018-jun-4-016.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2Fw600%2F201806%2F20180604120343_9_PCPU18040-2018-jun-4-016.jpg&h=687dac04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可是這個做法其實不太必要，加上遮樣錯失可能會錯失蝦碌鏡頭，感覺是改良但得不到合適效果。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/w600/201806/20180604120343_10_PCPU18040-2018-jun-4-014.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2Fw600%2F201806%2F20180604120343_10_PCPU18040-2018-jun-4-014.jpg&h=8bde22ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/w600/201806/20180604120343_11_PCPU18040-2018-jun-4-015.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2Fw600%2F201806%2F20180604120343_11_PCPU18040-2018-jun-4-015.jpg&h=7186b2a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>美女學徒似老臨</strong><br />\n《美女廚房》另一賣點就是美女學徒，不過今輯的美女學徒淪為臨時演員，在後排負責賣笑，得閒才會有一、兩個鏡頭，反而以前特別介紹、有Catwalk更好睇。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/w600/201806/20180604120343_12_PCPU18040-2018-jun-4-011.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2Fw600%2F201806%2F20180604120343_12_PCPU18040-2018-jun-4-011.jpg&h=aedb0d4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n只見美女學徒好似佈景版。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/w600/201806/20180604120343_13_PCPU18040-2018-jun-4-046.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2Fw600%2F201806%2F20180604120343_13_PCPU18040-2018-jun-4-046.jpg&h=d87bd1e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>評審嘉賓更適合做主持</strong><br />\n第一集嘉賓是農夫，他們最會帶動氣氛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/w600/201806/20180604120343_14_PCPU18040-2018-jun-4-048.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2Fw600%2F201806%2F20180604120343_14_PCPU18040-2018-jun-4-048.jpg&h=4d2c3102&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n他們是不少網民收睇《美女廚房》的主因，今集已見他們盡力地搞笑，可是節目還是有點悶。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/w600/201806/20180604120343_15_PCPU18040-2018-jun-4-069.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2Fw600%2F201806%2F20180604120343_15_PCPU18040-2018-jun-4-069.jpg&h=998289e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n假如他們做主持的話，應該會更放，比較有追看性。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/w600/201806/20180604120343_16_PCPU18040-2018-jun-4-080.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2Fw600%2F201806%2F20180604120343_16_PCPU18040-2018-jun-4-080.jpg&h=1518f845&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c340d082eb8a85019d6d6102820b85e31e730a55","tid":689773,"uid":140538,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T10:22:28.000Z","msg":"而我不知道邊個係張振朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到個主持班底就唔想睇"},{"pid":"a8d4ab978b12770237ff59872b532c6a30ac126c","tid":689773,"uid":2736,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T10:26:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f9527ea1bc0035bfd8e20c6fe2e361b9793adefb","tid":689773,"uid":38904,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T10:37:36.000Z","msg":"美女廚房3依啲垃圾節目who fucking cares?"},{"pid":"a4e3bdfe46f2c7f75ac600ec8ddd70a2af0ce0d1","tid":689773,"uid":3647,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"a8d4ab978b12770237ff59872b532c6a30ac126c","tid":689773,"uid":2736,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T10:26:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}